claim().notice: Claim ETH dividends.You can claim even if you already unstaked you SIR.

collectFeesAndStartAuction(address).notice: It cannot fail if the dividends transfer fails or payment to the winner fails.

contributorMintAndStake().notice: Auxiliary function for minting SIR rewards and staking them immediately in one call

getAuctionLot(address,address).notice: Winner of the auction can call this function to get the auction lot.If the transfer of the auction lot fails it reverts and the dividends (WETH) are not distributed, allowing the bidder to try again later.

lPerMintAndStake(uint256).notice: Auxiliary function for minting SIR rewards and staking them immediately in one call

stake(uint80).notice: Stakes SIR tokensTokens can be unstaked at any time.Your tokens must be staked during a dividend payment to receive ETH dividends

unstakeAndClaim(uint80).notice: Convenient function for unstaking SIR and claim ETH dividens in one call.
